jmplib.util

Class WrapperClassGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmplib.util.WrapperClassGenerator

  • public class WrapperClassGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to generate source code of wrapper classes. This class encapsulates dynamic code into classes to compile them and invoke the dynamic code.
    Author:
    Ignacio Lagartos
